thread.title_full: Nengun Performance について 投稿者 J. Reyes

author: J. Reyes
title: J. Reyes
text: I order the TRD louvers for my Scion FRS early in February 2017. They were quick to process my order and are allows sending emails in regards to status updates on the product. I received it two weeks later well-packaged. Bonus is that they sold the item way lower than other sites. Would highly recommend if you're shopping around for JDM products.
